OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry and
OL,6,Fsettled on Sunday with heat building,
OL,7,Fperhaps peaking on Tuesday, with some
OL,8,Fmuggy intervening nights. This heat
OL,9,Fperhaps triggering thunderstorms by
OL,10,Fthis time.
